Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:21.14,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身披天马圣衣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:23.91,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:27.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛若流星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:31.64,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无迟疑的双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:33.71,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泛着泪光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:38.02,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不含一丝阴翳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:40.56,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纵使遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:43.13,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纵使身死战地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:47.52,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了跨越那障壁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:50.12,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们坚定不移
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:51.84,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如星辰般闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:53.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星座起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:55.57,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:00:57.08,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作指引胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:00.58,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.65,0:01:03.40,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那有限的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:06.06,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧不息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:07.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们至深的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:09.19,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现明晰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那未知的极限的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:14.22,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是友情编织成的神话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:15.52,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:19.56,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣字幕组&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫龙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人的小宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈宾格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们用生命为代价
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我们开辟了前路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了女神雅典娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们这些尚存的圣斗士们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫龙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们所流的血 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会白费
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我们 唯有前进一途
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 怎么都是蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随随便便就舍弃自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗留下来的意志！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伟大的圣斗士的教诲！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好严重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟发生了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 虽然能感觉到小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫龙 贵鬼和不动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都消失到到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许珀里翁的圣剑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天地崩灭斩的残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这里到底发生了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Athena Exclamation…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一体放出的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究极的战法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于太过强力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从神话时代起就被雅典娜所禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险招式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 许珀里翁是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位黄金圣斗士不集结全力就无法打倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此强大的敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 他们三人去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵鬼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不动先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与许珀里翁同归于尽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我至今为止一直认为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗不取胜就毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那三人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把未来托付给了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜献出生命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜打破圣斗士的准则
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 并不是胜负这么简单的事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫龙 贵鬼和不动 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.93,0:05:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教会了我们这些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真正的圣斗士啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错呢 昴君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须前进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿着三位黄金圣斗士所开辟的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那条道路 是如何险阻崎岖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会将父亲的教诲铭刻于心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奋战到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托付给谁什么的 只是弱者的辩解而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有屡战屡胜 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是真正的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小宇宙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许珀里翁！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许珀里翁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才不愧为号称四天王之中最强武人的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃下一记Athena Exclamation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然活着吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是不死身吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那种程度的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在身披这身崩灭刻衣的许珀里翁我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无作用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使集合三位黄金圣斗士的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只是毁坏了圣剑而已吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能将我这天地崩灭斩彻底击毁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是黄金圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的力量 觉悟 与斗志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是值得称赞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 终究非我敌手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区人类竟胆敢毁坏伟大神祗赐予的圣剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更是罪该万死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就给我以死赎罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 明知毫无胜算 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却仍要做无谓的挣扎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话 谁要老老实实地等着送死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集三名黄金之力都未能将我击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还妄想同我正面对抗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了圣剑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如同失去了利齿的猛兽一般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且事实是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位黄金圣斗士已经将你逼入了绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要继承他们三人的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲曾教诲我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们互相着想的心意与小宇宙交融之时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会创造出无限的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是凭借这种力量打倒了高卢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让你见识一下 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 这就是Ω的皮毛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我也不会手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想动我分毫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不够看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这小宇宙强得不科学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然纹丝未动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们竟然连碰都碰不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说他和之前的四天王根本不是一个级别的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与埃该翁以及高卢不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们或对人类抱有浓厚的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或视人类为虫豸 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以玩弄人类为乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这想法实在天真可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我对你们不抱有任何感情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想将你们杀得体无完肤 彻底击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起同高卢的战斗吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想攻我不备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭这种小伎俩 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想封住我的行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超新星爆！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕虫小技
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一招应该能行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马座…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 终于能近我身了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马回旋碎击拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 只有这种程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.93,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼近圣斗士的最大危机！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒了Ω的皮毛 却只有这点实力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不够看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本毫无胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:12:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们合力出击 竟然都无法打败他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙明明已经没有圣剑了 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还拥有那么强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如同你们失去了同伴一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也被夺去了无可替代之物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是这种极限状态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我变得更加强大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可替代之物？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是埃该翁和高卢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 我说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孱弱之辈 根本入不了我的眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴战死 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然无动于衷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可替代之物 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必说 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指的自然是天地崩灭斩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是某位大人赐予我的 忠诚的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就由我 将你们圣斗士的证明 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些圣衣粉碎得渣都不剩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究是区区人类 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太脆弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 许珀里翁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然觉得圣剑比并肩作战的同伴更加重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴 不要乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓武人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纵使孤军奋战 也要全力争胜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那几个黄金圣斗士 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎以为三位一体的战法就是展现了真正的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不过是弱者的垂死挣扎罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少扯淡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要继续相信什么同伴之情 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就永远无法超越我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是紫龙 贵鬼还是不动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是为我们指引了前路的伟大圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:14:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许你侮辱他们拼上生命的觉悟！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为失去同伴而悔恨不已 是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道就没有这种重要的同伴吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群软弱的乌合之众 能成什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有什么值得信赖的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所信赖的 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有将圣剑赐予我的 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位伟大的存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伟大的存在？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是帕拉斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所效忠的并非帕拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们就要丧命于此了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也信仰着女神雅典娜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心有不甘的话 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后就让我见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的忠诚之心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没等看完我的招式 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就来飞蛾扑火了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 没想到正面吃了我一击 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还有负隅顽抗的力气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是普通的圣斗士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名为昴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是要成为神的男人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴那家伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然让迄今为止一步都没动的许珀里翁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后退了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 在与高卢的战斗中也感受到过的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异常强大的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比那时的小宇宙更强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的小鬼还想成为神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这巨大的小宇宙甚至能联想到神 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可能 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成为神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一直都是我的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类也意外地不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算一个人的力量很渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴的力量汇聚起来 也会成为庞大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 可以引发不可想象的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从遇到这些家伙之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我目睹了很多这奇迹的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都拥有着强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会引发奇迹的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引发谁人都从未达成的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类都是脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是圣斗士 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是也会轻易死亡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许确实是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使肉体毁灭 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的意志依旧永存
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有继承他们想法的同伴存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}昴君…穿上我的…钢铁圣衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}知道的话就说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}这个就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}昴你一定能逆转这圣衣的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类为同伴着想的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远比你所认为的更加强大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份思念的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是绝对不会输给瞧不起同伴的你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴的小宇宙 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压倒了许珀里翁的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是什么时候得到那么强的力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是人类的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是神的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底为什么有这种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能威胁到那位大人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一律消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会将你的时间与空间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这世界上抹杀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有圣剑 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹杀区区你这小子的时间还是绰绰有余的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招 时光毁灭！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓唬我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说要成为神？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是一介渺小的人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才发生了异常的小宇宙增大现象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来时机越来越近了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 欧罗巴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是放任他逃跑 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰河
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经无路可逃了 欧罗巴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 终于万事休矣了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该老实交代了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在谋划什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你假作逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借以扰乱我们的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赚取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 已经晚了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人的觉醒已经临近了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的对手 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会转交给其他人代为担当的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 诸位传说中的圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥是米拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来打发时间的圣衣破坏娱乐已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那位大人就要降临
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥也终于能认真起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人觉醒的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已经接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 快来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们做个了断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.24,0:22:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经死了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神明所言的 对人类来说过于强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 但凡人类 皆少量拥有的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.03,0:22:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以24个希腊字母的最后一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执掌终结的字母为名的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是我们的目标 究极的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话 圣斗士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究极的Ω！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在吗？
